Design a professional insurance department dashboard interface after login.

Style: clean, modern government / enterprise web application UI, minimal, professional, high readability.

Layout:
- Top horizontal header with insurance department logo on the left
- Welcome text with user name and role (Insurance Officer)
- Notification bell icon and logout button on the right

Left sidebar navigation:
- Dashboard
- Policy Management
- Customers
- Claims
- Reports & Analytics
- Settings
Use simple icons and a light background sidebar

Main content area:
- Dashboard overview with 4 summary cards:
  • Active Policies
  • Pending Claims
  • Premium Collected
  • Policies Expiring Soon
- Cards should have soft shadows, rounded corners, and subtle icons

Below summary cards:
- Recent Claims table with columns:
  Claim ID, Customer Name, Policy Type, Status
- Status badges in green (approved), yellow (pending), red (rejected)

Quick action buttons:
- Create Policy
- Register Customer
- File Claim
- View Reports

Color theme:
- White background
- Light blue and navy accents
- Soft gray dividers
- Professional government portal look

Typography:
- Clean sans-serif font
- Clear hierarchy for headings and labels

Output:
- High-resolution web dashboard UI
- Desktop view
- Realistic production-ready design


